ὀφείλω καὶ δοῦν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">α</supplied>ι τῷ Ὥρῳ καὶ <choice><corr>Εὐδαίμονι</corr><sic>ευδαιμονει</sic></choice> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἑ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">κατέρῳ</unclear> ἐπὰν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὦσι</unclear> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἐ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῶν<num value="20">κ</num>δραχμὰ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ς</unclear> <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">π</supplied>εν-

